name: Si Señor Peruvian Sandwiches and More

reviews.text: We loved everything!  I can't believe I've never been before--they didn't have plantains or empanadas (would have ordered both), but what we did have was...
Si Señor makes some darn good sandwiches. And the cilantro cream pasta is delicious. I've gotten a combo both times, which comes with a sandwich and chips...
Awesome sandwiches and salads! Everyone I've introduced to them also loves them. Just something special about their food. My favorite is the Chicharron...
